{
  "stem": "24814.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what was done about notifying kin, if they could find them, or burying them or what, you know, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were so concerned with trying to save them-- the living that we just knew that, when people died, they were whisked off someplace.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't-- till you asked me that question, I hadn't thought about that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But there was a bewildering variety of backgrounds when you talk to these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they all spoke some German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since I speak fluent German, I did a lot of interpreting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A Pole would talk to a Czech, would talked with this, would talk to me, and they'd go back down the chain so they could all communicate with each other.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because like-- like most infections, except AIDS and rabies, a certain number of people will always recover.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- immune body, even under those conditions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially the ones that hadn't been starved that long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, you had all degrees of starvation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people had only been there a month, and they were pretty thin, but they weren't terminally starved.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had a much better chance of living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were pretty-- they didn't want us running around the camp, because we were in the typhus center.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even though we had typhus shots, and we'd put DDT, there was an idea, stay where you are, don't go around and look at the rest of the building.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've seen pictures of the gas chambers and the-- the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't actually see them myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not encouraged to wander around when we were in the typhus center.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I'm trying to think now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So many stories I heard from these people, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
